room_title: Escape room "Myth of the West" by Epic Escape Game in Cheyenne
room_description: The American West 1867. Pioneers, outlaws & bandits pushed their way westward in search of land, gold and silver. You and your gang just entered the Cheyenne Saloon to have a drink when the door slams shut behind you. This is the infamous Wild Bunch's territory and they don't take kindly to strangers. You have only 1 hour to escape the saloon before the Wild Bunch returns.
